r />\n天台晚餐 自己保重 我都係近排睇故先知呢兩首歌 一首冧歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一首分手歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iyDYMcKc_L0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiyDYMcKc_L0&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu16hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=1c35d752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iyDYMcKc_L0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hK1GAnqDRAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhK1GAnqDRAo&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu16hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=6fc5cd23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hK1GAnqDRAo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有點少啲聖誕歌 分分鐘可以屌打連登主題曲last christmas <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ahOgvDGZzmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FahOgvDGZzmQ&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu16hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=9f0bb876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ahOgvDGZzmQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rfMa6SHsuzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrfMa6SHsuzI&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu16hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=30b36218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rfMa6SHsuzI</a>"},{"pid":"e0d3ce56a87d05445ecb94277b8c934507b3e811","tid":1017424,"uid":90316,"like":10,"dislike":9,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p5yTF23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5yTF23.png&h=31bf8f51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amWU9Wq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamWU9Wq.png&h=d30bbe1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXqiR9M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXqiR9M.png&h=5910354e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係好鍾意juno 又厭世又型 好想瘋狂磨佢個光頭仔<img src=\"/a